# Build Bible V2 — Chapter 13 (Enterprise Regression)

Spec: `docs/15_BUILD_BIBLE_V2_CHAPTER_13_REGRESSION.md`

## Rules

- Use `scripts/_test-helpers/read-source.mjs` for new source-contract tests — do not duplicate `rootDir`/`readSource`.
- Keep `ENTERPRISE_REGRESSION_SUITE` as the curated release-confidence catalog.
- Prefer source-contract assertions of existing wiring over changing product behaviour.
- Do not modify business logic, authentication, authorization, RBAC, RLS, Paddle billing behaviour, or API contracts for test convenience.
- Do not redesign UI or add features unless required to eliminate a proven regression.
- Playwright smoke includes password-reset; authenticated suites may skip without credentials — CI should treat missing credentials as incomplete coverage, not success theatre.

## This chapter

- Do not commit, push, or deploy from Chapter 13 work.
